            "back": "Bitmap uses pixels, vector uses maths"
        },
        {
            "front": "What is lossy compression?",
            "back": "Compression that reduces quality"
        },
        {
            "front": "What is lossless compression?",
            "back": "Compression with no quality loss"
        },
        {
            "front": "What is a pixel?",
